item.title: Welcome to KayEssPea Blog!
item.description: Hello, and welcome to my new blog! I decided that I wanted a blog, and so here it is. This will predomenently be a design and web development blog. I love to teach, and I like to write. So, I figured there’d be no better place to write the things I want to teach.
